- [ ] rgba() preserves all components
- [ ] Component accessors round-trip
- [ ] over() with opaque src returns src
- [ ] over() with transparent src returns dst
- [ ] over() blends correctly for 50% alpha
- [ ] with_opacity() scales alpha correctly

